<L>La&s;t of the motley bands on whom the pow'r<NOTE PLACE="foot">&vers;. 228. <HI>La&s;t of the,</HI> &amp;c.] Ridicule from the ignorance of &s;uch things as our circum&s;tances require us to know.</NOTE></L>
