<L N="255">She darts advent'rous up the long career</L>
<L>Of comets, thro' the con&s;tellations holds</L>
<L>Her cour&s;e, and now looks back on all the &s;tars,</L>
<L>Who&s;e blended flames as with a milky &s;tream</L>
<L>Part the blue region. Empyrean tracks,</L>
<L N="260">Where happy &s;ouls beyond this concave heav'n</L>
