<L><PB N="126" REF="126">
For countle&s;s ages travels thro' th' aby&s;s,</L>
<L>Nor hath in &s;ight of mortals yet arriv'd:</L>
<L>Upon the wide creation's utmo&s;t &s;hore</L>
<L N="265">At length &s;he &s;tands, and the dread &s;pace beyond</L>
<L>Contemplates, half recoiling; nathle&s;s down</L>
<L>The gloomy void a&s;toni&s;h'd yet unquell'd</L>
<L>She plungeth, down th' unfathomable gulf</L>
<L>Where God alone hath being; there her hopes</L>
<L N="270">Re&s;t at the fated goal: for from the birth</L>
<L>Of humankind the Sovran Maker &s;aid</L>
