<L>Expatiate with glad &s;tep, and chu&s;e at will</L>
<L>Whate'er bright &s;poils the florid earth contains,</L>
<L N="300">Whate'er the waters or the liquid air,</L>
<L>To manife&s;t unblemi&s;h'd Beauty's prai&s;e,</L>
