<L>Lo! Beauty withers in your void embrace,</L>
<L N="445">And with the glitt'ring of an idiot's toy</L>
<L>Did fancy mock your vows. Nor yet let hope,</L>
<L>That kindlie&s;t inmate of the youthful brea&s;t,</L>
